                          RANGER'S GUILD HELP
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
COMMAND:             DESCRIPTION:
--------             ------------
ranhelp              Shows this screen. Do 'ranhelp <command/topic>' for
                     further info on most things. You may use 'rh' in
                     place of 'ranhelp'.
rangers              Shows what Rangers are currently on.
rangerbug <message>  Reports a bug about Rangers.
ran <message>        Chats on the Ranger Guild line.
eran <message>       Emotes on the Ranger Guild line.
skills               Shows your current skills.
bio                  Shows your personal Ranger bio.
slots/slots #        Shows how many slots you have and available skills for
                     you.
recruit <name>       Recruits another player into the guild. They have to
                     accept.
rebuild quiver       If you have lost your quiver, you can get a new one
                     with this command.
repair quiver        Refreshes your quiver if you are having problems.
motto <motto>        Declares your motto which is seen on the rangers screen.
improve <what>       Advances stats and your level.
cost                 Shows current costs for advancing.
journal              Lists available quests.
learn <skill>        Lets you learns a new skill.
check <terrain>      Checks what skills are available to be learned or used
		     in that terrain.


ADDITIONAL TOPICS:   glevels terrains stats archery weapons armour
                     emotes followers enemy alignment history skills

TERRAINS:            forest plains swamp desert jungle city hills sea
                     lake river road dock inside beach underground
                     mountain arctic barren underwater
